    "sn18.12-20:6.6": "dhammasañcetanā …. ",
    "sn18.12-20:7.1": "Rūpataṇhā …pe… ",
    "sn18.12-20:7.2": "saddataṇhā … ",
    "sn18.12-20:7.3": "gandhataṇhā … ",
    "sn18.12-20:7.4": "rasataṇhā … ",
    "sn18.12-20:7.5": "phoṭṭhabbataṇhā … ",
    "sn18.12-20:7.6": "dhammataṇhā …. ",
    "sn18.12-20:8.1": "Pathavīdhātu …pe… ",
    "sn18.12-20:8.2": "āpodhātu … ",
    "sn18.12-20:8.3": "tejodhātu … ",
    "sn18.12-20:8.4": "vāyodhātu … ",
    "sn18.12-20:8.5": "ākāsadhātu … ",
    "sn18.12-20:8.6": "viññāṇadhātu …. ",
    "sn18.12-20:9.1": "Rūpaṁ …pe… ",
    "sn18.12-20:9.2": "vedanā … ",
    "sn18.12-20:9.3": "saññā … ",
    "sn18.12-20:9.4": "saṅkhārā … ",
    "sn18.12-20:9.5": "viññāṇaṁ niccaṁ vā aniccaṁ vā”ti? ",
    "sn18.12-20:9.6": "Aniccaṁ, bhante …pe… ",
    "sn18.12-20:9.7": "“evaṁ passaṁ rāhula …pe… ",
    "sn18.12-20:9.8": "nāparaṁ itthattāyā’ti pajānātī”ti. ",
    "sn18.12-20:9.9": "Dasamaṁ. "
